{
  "id": "10239",
  "key": "GG-236",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Redesign UI/UX for Login and Migrate",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a developer, I want to redesign the login UI/UX and migrate user data to improve usability and align with modern design standards."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Description:",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The login screen should be redesigned to provide a more intuitive, responsive, and modern user interface. This includes improving the layout, typography, and interactions. Additionally, the migration of user data (credentials, preferences) should be handled securely to ensure a seamless transition to the new design. The goal is to enhance the user experience and align the login flow with current design trends while ensuring data integrity during the migration process."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance Criteria:",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The login UI is redesigned with a focus on simplicity and usability (e.g., clear input fields, concise labels, and minimal distractions)."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The new design aligns with the platform’s overall branding (colors, fonts, and visual elements)."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The new design is reviewed and approved by the design team and key stakeholders."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Dependencies:",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "UI/UX design approval."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Feedback from stakeholders and end users on the new design."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Business Value:",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Improving the login experience will reduce friction for users, enhance user satisfaction, and modernize the platform’s entry point, which could lead to higher user retention and engagement."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
